          The Project (Tamweelcom 3) entails an IFC investment to the Jordan Micro Credit Company (Tamweelcom or the Company). The purpose of the loan is to support Tamweelcom to increase lending to individual entrepreneurs, micro and very small enterprises (VSEs) in Jordan. The project will contribute to increased access to finance to underserved segments of the countrys economy, including women entrepreneurs, financial inclusion and creation of new business opportunities.

